grunt, gulp -> tools ->
  task runners
    * optimization (css)
    * compilation (scss->css)
    * concat of files (.js)
    * uglify (compress)
    * image processing

1) npm install -g grunt-cli
2) npm install grunt --save-dev
3) create Gruntfile.js -> tasks+config
4) src/   -> source code (scss, less, js ...)
5) dist/  -> production
6) grunt (less)
    * npm install grunt-contrib-less --save-dev

    * npm install grunt-autoprefixer --save-dev
